This can be done without making use of an additional class with a combination of both the [`:not`][1] *and* the [`:nth-of-type()`][2] (or [`:nth-child()`][3]) pseudo-classes:

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-css --&gt;

    body {
      counter-reset: section;
    }

    p:not(:nth-of-type(5)):before {
      counter-increment: section;
      content: &quot;&quot; counter(section) &quot;: &quot;;
